AvaSoft 8.5.0

Release Date (yyyy-mm-dd): 2016-06-30

Changes / New features:

- Added support for Single Scan Triggering for EVO spectrometers
- Demo mode added that runs without a spectrometer attached
- Averaging is now allowed in StoreToRam mode


Bug fixes:

- Merging mode was improved
- Export to Excel was improved
- Splining mode was improved


    

